# Root .dockerignore — applied when building from the repository root.
# Keeps host-only artifacts out of every build context so native deps
# resolved on the host (e.g. bcrypt, ioredis) don't leak into the
# container image.

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
.claude

docs
docs/**
SCRATCHPAD.md
**/SCRATCHPAD.md

**/Thumbs.db
**/.DS_Store
